When I try to follow the linux CPU tests (python 3) and ci.tensorflow.org link to look at the reason for CI failure I get the following:
```
HTTP ERROR 404
Problem accessing /job/tensorflow-pull-requests-multijob/8773/. Reason:

    Not Found

```
Do you need to re-run jenkins or something?
